## Quick facts

- Stack: Astro 7 static SSG + Svelte 5 islands → GitHub Pages (`gh-pages`)
- Docs: `SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md`, `.github/copilot-instructions.md`
- Tools CRUD: content MDX + Svelte island + `src/pages/tools/[id]/index.astro` registry
- AI / STT / ASR / diarization / meeting minutes: `@ai-speech-meeting-tools`
- Security / privacy / governance: `@security-anti-patterns`, `@agent-governance`, `@privacy-third-parties`

